mayn mame, yo, m'hot shoyn gehert az me darf undz firn in a shtot, ale yidn

00:09:40.967 --> 00:09:43.863
un mayn mame hot zikh gevolt a bisl esn mitnemen

00:09:43.903 --> 00:09:47.545
hot zi zikh arayngeganvet dort in dem vu s'iz geven di tvue

00:09:47.545 --> 00:09:49.435
un zi hot mit a shtikl holts

00:09:49.435 --> 00:09:53.835
a bisl gemakht tvue, a halb zekl tvue, me zol mitnemen, zol hobn vos tsu esn.

00:09:54.484 --> 00:09:57.624
un s'iz gekumen nokh a, dos gedenk ikh nisht vifl

00:09:57.624 --> 00:10:00.124
iz gekumen, m'hot undz ge- UNK -kumen a fur

