00:10:59.352 --> 00:11:01.658
vu iz geven der bruder mit der shvester?

00:11:00.904 --> 00:11:02.754
der bruder mit di shvester iz geven in shtub.

00:11:03.081 --> 00:11:05.461
yo. di shvester, zi iz geven mer

00:11:05.461 --> 00:11:10.621
a gelernte, hot zi geleyent mer bikher, hot zi gehat dort a Lemberiker. zi hot zikh mit dem nisht farnumen azoy vi ikh.

00:11:10.860 --> 00:11:14.873
ikh bin geven zeyer a gute tokhter fun der mame. di mame hot mir zeyer lib gehat.

00:11:14.873 --> 00:11:18.346
un dernokh dem vel ikh oyfdekn vos iz gevezn, yo?

00:11:16.783 --> 00:11:17.722
yo.

00:11:18.673 --> 00:11:20.180
shpeter

00:11:20.180 --> 00:11:24.804
iz gekumen vos s'hot shoyn ongehoybn di yidn shlekht tsu vern vos a mol erger un erger.

00:11:24.804 --> 00:11:29.538
s'iz nokh geven dem ershtn peysekh, vos m'hot afile gekrign tsu dray matses oyf peysekh.

00:11:29.538 --> 00:11:30.970
dos gedenk ikh oykhet.

00:11:31.448 --> 00:11:35.638
nokh dem, dakht zikh dos iz nokh peysekh, geven di ershte aktsye

00:11:35.638 --> 00:11:40.008
vos m'hot genumen di yunge mentshn hot men genumen in di lagern tsu arbetn.

00:11:39.953 --> 00:11:44.503
dos iz, oyb ir redt shoyn, antshuldikn, oyb ir redt shoyn vegn peysekh

00:11:40.510 --> 00:11:42.107
ikh bin, yo

00:11:44.970 --> 00:11:46.270
dos iz geven

00:11:45.066 --> 00:11:47.929
iz di daytshn zenen arayn⟨gekumen⟩ zumertsayt

00:11:48.087 --> 00:11:52.975
peysekh iz shoyn, haltn mir shoyn bay, azoy merts april tsvey un fertsik.

00:11:52.845 --> 00:11:55.977
dos iz geven tsvey un fertsik, yo, dos iz geven tsvey un fertsik.

00:11:53.217 --> 00:11:55.084
mer veyniker. ts- yo.

00:11:55.275 --> 00:11:56.163
yo.

00:11:56.203 --> 00:11:58.964
dernokh dem hobn zey gemakht a aktsye

00:11:58.971 --> 00:12:04.393
un m'hot arumgeringlt di shtot, un me hot genumen nor di yunge m- bakhurim tsu di arbet

00:12:04.393 --> 00:12:06.120
tsu ⟨Korevitsher⟩ lager.

00:12:07.307 --> 00:12:10.627
un mayn bruder hot men gekhapt oykhet. m'hot im gekhapt

00:12:10.627 --> 00:12:16.487
un er iz geven dortn nisht lang. dos gedenk ikh nisht vifl, tsi er iz geven dort a monat, tsi er iz geven

00:12:16.487 --> 00:12:17.797
tsvey vokhn

00:12:17.955 --> 00:12:20.627
un er iz geven eyn eyntsiker zun oykhet

00:12:20.627 --> 00:12:23.065
vos er iz geven in der heym gepyeshtshet.

00:12:23.065 --> 00:12:25.290
di mame hot im oykhet zeyer lib gehat

00:12:25.414 --> 00:12:26.370
yo

00:12:26.410 --> 00:12:30.430
iz er antlofn. er hot UNK im ⟨gelungen⟩ tsu antloyfn. ⟨er hot⟩ gekumen in shtub arayn

00:12:30.430 --> 00:12:34.150
oyf azoy er hot antlo- un far dem, yo, ⟨az s'iz⟩ gekumen di daytshn

00:12:34.150 --> 00:12:38.722
un m'hot gezogt tsu undz "tomer me khapt nisht dayn zun, harget men undz ale oys," yo?

00:12:39.117 --> 00:12:46.249
azoy undz hobn mir gevart vos vet geshen mit undz. dervayl iz gekumen. dernokh dem hot men undz gezogt az dem bruder hot men gekhapt, un me hot im oyfgehongen.

00:12:46.862 --> 00:12:52.897
m'hot anfang di mame nisht dertseylt. undz ho'mir gevust fun dem, oder di mame hot nisht dervust a shtikl tsayt az im hot men oyfgehongen.

00:12:53.157 --> 00:12:55.516
oder dernokhdem hot zi gevoyr gevorn

00:12:55.516 --> 00:12:59.226
iz zi gevorn shtark krank. zi hot shtark ibergelebt, iz zi gelign in bet.

00:12:59.721 --> 00:13:03.714
un nokh dem iz shoyn gevorn vos a mol erger di yidn.

00:13:04.041 --> 00:13:08.220
es iz gevorn a aktsye. vi azoy iz di aktsye geven?

00:13:08.344 --> 00:13:11.966
di daytshn hobn arumgeringlt arum un arum di shtot

00:13:12.411 --> 00:13:15.711
un a yidisher politsyant iz gegangen

00:13:15.711 --> 00:13:19.391
meldn me zol nemen oyf dray tog esn mit koldres

00:13:19.391 --> 00:13:22.180
mitnemen. di esn iz avade nisht gevezn

00:13:22.180 --> 00:13:24.190
un m'vet forn tsu di arbet, yo?

00:13:24.662 --> 00:13:28.800
un mayn mame hot dokh shoyn gevust vos se vart, az dos iz nisht emes.

00:13:28.852 --> 00:13:33.155
zi iz geven krank, hot zi mikh gerufn tsum bet un zi hot gezogt "veys vos?

00:13:33.155 --> 00:13:35.214
du bist mayn beste kind.

00:13:35.214 --> 00:13:38.527
ikh ⟨vil⟩, du antloyf in dorf STRILKY

00:13:38.685 --> 00:13:42.088
un ikh vel oyf dir oysbetn ⟨vos⟩ du vest lebn blaybn."

00:13:42.195 --> 00:13:43.758
zogt zi "gey antloyf."

00:13:44.220 --> 00:13:48.686
hob ikh gehorkht. ikh gedenk nisht vu mayn shvester iz geven. dos gedenk ikh bikhlal nisht.

00:13:49.080 --> 00:13:50.609
hob ikh genumen

00:13:50.616 --> 00:13:54.424
un ikh hob aroysgegangen, un di daytshn zenen geshtanen arum un arum

00:13:54.565 --> 00:13:55.734
arumgeringlt.

00:13:55.734 --> 00:13:57.849
un ikh bin gekumen. di daytshn

00:13:57.957 --> 00:14:00.904
es makht er azoy mitn hant "HALT" tsu mir.

00:14:01.146 --> 00:14:06.877
hob ikh ongehoybn tsu im redn ukraynish, vayl ukraynish hob ikh gekent, vayl ikh hob gelernt ⟨in⟩ a ukraynishe shule

00:14:06.883 --> 00:14:08.969
un ikh zog im oyf ukraynish

00:14:09.077 --> 00:14:11.807
ikh ken dos zogn ukraynish, ikh ken dos zogn yidish

00:14:11.807 --> 00:14:13.408
"ikh leb dortn.

00:14:13.701 --> 00:14:15.588
dortn iz mayn voynung," yo?

00:14:15.588 --> 00:14:17.846
der daytsh hot gornisht nisht gezogt

00:14:17.869 --> 00:14:19.199
nor er hot gezogt "gey."

00:14:19.199 --> 00:14:20.445
un ikh bin gegangen.

00:14:20.569 --> 00:14:22.869
undz ho'mir dort gehat bakante goyim.

00:14:22.869 --> 00:14:24.489
ikh bin gekumen tsun a goye

00:14:24.489 --> 00:14:25.746
un ikh hob ir gezogt

00:14:25.746 --> 00:14:27.651
"vayzt vos iz di aktsye?

00:14:27.775 --> 00:14:32.325
kenst mir haltn. ikh vel bay dir arbetn, vos du vilst nor, vel ikh bay dir arbetn."

00:14:32.753 --> 00:14:34.766
zogt zi "gut. s'iz yetst di shnit

00:14:34.766 --> 00:14:36.983
un d'vest helfn di tvue aropnemen undz."

00:14:37.005 --> 00:14:38.771
hob ikh ongehoybn tsu arbetn.

00:14:39.030 --> 00:14:42.960
yedn in der fri bin ikh oyfgeshtanen zeyer fri ven s'iz nokh geven fintster.

00:14:42.960 --> 00:14:47.910
m'hot genumen ale UNK. m'iz gegangen. m'hot di shnit aropgenumen. ikh hob zeyer gut gekent arbetn.

00:14:47.912 --> 00:14:49.537
es hot zey zeyer gefoln.

00:14:49.662 --> 00:14:52.288
ikh hob dort opgearbet a vokh tsayt.

00:14:52.463 --> 00:14:53.908
nokh a vokh

00:14:54.066 --> 00:14:57.047
iz di shnur gegangen keyn Boyberik.

00:14:57.559 --> 00:15:02.618
iz zi gekumen fun Boyberik, hot zi mikh tsugerufn, "zol gevis-" zogt zi azoy. "veystu vos

00:15:02.618 --> 00:15:06.491
yetst kenstu tsurikgeyn. vemen m'hot geharget hot men geharget.

00:15:06.491 --> 00:15:09.110
ver s'iz geblibn lebn ken yetst geyn tsurik.

00:15:09.110 --> 00:15:10.270
⟨ir vet⟩ blaybn lebn.

00:15:10.270 --> 00:15:12.990
yetst tshepet nisht. UNK yetst tut men gornisht di yidn."

00:15:13.843 --> 00:15:17.620
hot zi mir genumen. zi hot mir gegebn a zekl tvue far di arbet

00:15:17.620 --> 00:15:18.900
zogt zi "gey yetst.

00:15:18.900 --> 00:15:20.980
un ikh hob genumen di zekl tvue.

00:15:20.980 --> 00:15:23.020
ikh hob gegangen tsu di arbet, oder vos iz?

00:15:23.020 --> 00:15:25.104
ikh hob geshlofn dort oyfn boydem

00:15:25.104 --> 00:15:27.675
un ikh hob tsuri- ikh hob zeyer geveynt yede nakht.

00:15:27.698 --> 00:15:30.645
k- azoy vi ikh hob gefilt ikh vel keynem nisht trefn.

00:15:31.022 --> 00:15:32.720
ven ikh bin gekumen tsurik

00:15:32.720 --> 00:15:35.650
oyf mayn gas iz aroysgelofn a sakh kinder

00:15:35.650 --> 00:15:40.229
un zey hobn ongehoybn zogn "du veyst vos? dayn mame iz shoyn nishto. dayn mamen hot men derharget"

00:15:41.518 --> 00:15:43.756
un ikh hob shtark ongehoybn tsu veynen.

00:15:43.982 --> 00:15:45.849
ikh hob gekumen aheym

00:15:45.923 --> 00:15:47.604
un ikh hob gornisht getrofn.

00:15:47.745 --> 00:15:50.253
s'iz nor geven eyn alte froy

00:15:50.682 --> 00:15:55.418
vos ir zun iz geharget gevorn, vos er iz gelign in gas. zi hot shtark geveynt oykhet

00:15:55.542 --> 00:16:00.075
un vi azoy ikh veyn azoy, kumt tsu geyn a yidisher politsyant

00:16:01.026 --> 00:16:04.330
un er zogt azoy "du host dokh gearbet di gantse tsayt oyf mir."

00:16:04.330 --> 00:16:09.845
zog ikh "ikh hob gearbet far di mamen. ikh bin dokh nisht UNK, ikh bin dokh alt f- nokh nisht keyn fuftsn yor. ikh darf dokh nisht arbetn.

00:16:09.970 --> 00:16:13.288
zogt er "neyn, du muzt geyn arbetn, vayl s'iz nishto genug arbetn."

00:16:13.783 --> 00:16:18.183
un ikh hob nisht gevolt geyn. un er hot mir ongehoybn azoy tsu shlogn, hot mir shtark geshlogn.

00:16:18.183 --> 00:16:19.293
dos gedenk ikh.

00:16:19.470 --> 00:16:22.352
shpeter hot er mir shoyn azoy geshlogn vos ikh hob avekgefaln.

00:16:22.352 --> 00:16:24.476
ikh hob shtark geveynt, hot er mir gelozt.

00:16:24.972 --> 00:16:29.162
er hot mir gelozt, un ikh bin azoy geblibn legn, lign dortn

00:16:29.162 --> 00:16:32.258
iz tsugekumen tsu mir undzere a shokhnte

00:16:32.258 --> 00:16:34.030
un zi hot gezogt "veystu vos?

00:16:34.030 --> 00:16:40.729
baruik zikh. kum tsu mir. vest hobn bay mir arbet. d'vest pashen di ku. d'vest arbetn. d'vest dervayle lebn bay undz.

00:16:40.380 --> 00:16:41.770
a ukraynke.

00:16:40.729 --> 00:16:42.448
ikh, a ukraynke, yo.

00:16:43.365 --> 00:16:46.346
zey zenen geven a mishpokhe a raykhe

00:16:46.791 --> 00:16:49.020
vos zey hobn gehat a sakh farmegn, yo?

00:16:49.020 --> 00:16:50.660
iz zey hobn gehat zeyer a sakh arbet.

00:16:50.959 --> 00:16:53.050
zi hot mikh tsugenumen tsu zikh

00:16:53.050 --> 00:16:56.120
un ikh hob bald ongehoybn a sakh tsu arbetn.

00:16:56.393 --> 00:16:58.159
vos iz geven mayn arbet?

00:16:58.215 --> 00:17:01.045
koydem kol in der fri, dray a zeyger hot zi mir gevekt

00:17:01.045 --> 00:17:02.705
di ki tsu pashen, yo?

00:17:02.705 --> 00:17:05.499
hob ikh gepashet di ki. ikh hob shtendik geveynt dortn.

00:17:05.724 --> 00:17:07.827
ikh hob gekumen tsurik fun di ki

00:17:08.137 --> 00:17:10.367
hob ikh badorfn zey melkn.

00:17:10.367 --> 00:17:12.377
kh'hob badorfn holts tsugreytn.

00:17:12.377 --> 00:17:14.607
kh'hob badorfn di poln vashn.

00:17:14.607 --> 00:17:17.509
ale arbetn vos s'iz nor geven hot men mir gegebn.

00:17:17.509 --> 00:17:21.044
afile in stodole tsu z- tsu mloytsn tvue

00:17:21.044 --> 00:17:23.437
hob ikh oykhet gemloytset di tvue, yo?

00:17:23.798 --> 00:17:26.762
esn hot zi mir nisht a sakh gegebn.

00:17:26.768 --> 00:17:34.098
iz vos fleg ikh tun? ikh fleg tsuganvenen a shtikele broyt UNK zi hot nit gezen. ikh fleg arayngeyn in klozet, un ikh fleg dos broyt esn.

00:17:34.181 --> 00:17:36.434
oder a epl fleg ikh mit a shtekn

00:17:36.434 --> 00:17:38.614
kh'gedenk zi hot gehat a kupe mit epl

00:17:38.614 --> 00:17:42.994
fleg ikh mit dem shtekn nemen, aroysnemen di e- mit dem drot aroysnemen di epl.

00:17:43.018 --> 00:17:46.606
ikh hob arayngegangen in BET SHIMUSH. ikh hob zikh farmakht. ikh hob oyfgegesn di epl.

00:17:47.710 --> 00:17:51.460
un ikh hob azoy opgearbet, dos gedenk ikh nisht, a por monat bay ir.

00:17:51.460 --> 00:17:52.960
hob ikh opgearbet bay ir.

00:17:53.802 --> 00:17:56.580
dernokh dem, in eyn tog kumt zi tsu geyn

00:17:56.580 --> 00:17:59.920
zogt zi tsu mir azoy. "veyst vos? biz yetst hob ikh dikh gehaltn.

00:17:59.920 --> 00:18:02.818
yetst iz do shoyn a geto. yetst muzstu geyn in geto.

00:18:02.818 --> 00:18:04.544
yetst ken ikh dikh mer nisht haltn."

00:18:05.091 --> 00:18:07.768
tsvishn dem iz dort gekumen a goye

00:18:08.179 --> 00:18:10.825
nisht keyn alte, nor nisht keyn farheyrate nokh

00:18:10.825 --> 00:18:14.872
un zi hot gezogt "veyst vos? in Voliner gegnt iz do zeyer gute goyim.

00:18:15.334 --> 00:18:17.040
ikh vel dikh mitnemen ahin

00:18:17.040 --> 00:18:22.220
un ⟨dort⟩ UNK a shtik geyn, dos, zog azoy, du redt mit dem az dayn dorf iz dertrunken gevorn

00:18:22.220 --> 00:18:24.140
un du bist geblibn aleyn, host nisht keynem.

00:18:24.140 --> 00:18:26.020
veln zey dir mitnemen tsu di arbet

00:18:26.020 --> 00:18:27.520
un d'vest dortn arbetn."

00:18:28.108 --> 00:18:30.771
un ikh redt op mit ir, vi azoy, ven

00:18:30.771 --> 00:18:35.881
un ikh hob gehat di tvue, iz dokh tvue nisht azoy gut, hob ikh genumen di tvue far ⟨zhorne⟩

00:18:36.073 --> 00:18:40.235
kh'hob tsemoln di tvue. ⟨zhornes⟩ iz dokh geven. ikh hob gemakht mel fun dem.

00:18:40.798 --> 00:18:45.508
un demolst iz nokh geven lebn, ge- lebn geblibn mayn kuzin's a tokhter

00:18:45.508 --> 00:18:47.488
mitn foter nokh geblibn lebn

00:18:47.532 --> 00:18:50.074
hob ikh ir gezogt "veyst vos, Sore

00:18:50.097 --> 00:18:51.711
ikh hob a zekl mel

00:18:51.902 --> 00:18:55.442
un ikh darf hobn a por zakhn zolst mir gebn, vayl ikh bin naket un borves.

00:18:55.442 --> 00:18:58.190
ikh vel dir gebn di tvue. breng mir di un di zakhn

00:18:58.467 --> 00:18:59.676
farn forn."

