00:19:03.698 --> 00:19:09.078
shtivl mit zoyln holtserne hot zi mir gebrengt, yo? un ikh hob ir gegebn dos mel

00:19:09.078 --> 00:19:11.370
vayl demolst iz dokh geven zeyer tayer dos mel

00:19:12.017 --> 00:19:15.133
un di goye hot mir oyfgeneyt tsvey hemder

00:19:15.443 --> 00:19:19.284
un di goye hot mir nokh gegebn a paltn a varemen oykhet hot zi mir gegebn.

00:19:19.847 --> 00:19:21.832
in eyn tog

00:19:21.872 --> 00:19:23.739
dos iz geven farnakht

00:19:23.948 --> 00:19:31.147
ikh gedenk nisht vi azoy, ze'mir ongekumen tsu der statsye. tsi ikh hob geforn tsi m'iz gegangen tsu fus iz geven zibn kilometer, dos gedenk ikh shoyn nisht.

00:19:31.204 --> 00:19:35.520
m'iz gekumen tsu der statsye, un m'hot gevart oyfn tsug mit der goye

00:19:35.520 --> 00:19:39.922
un ikh hob shtark geven in a pakhed az emetser derkent mikh fun mayn dorf, vayl dos iz geven

00:19:40.232 --> 00:19:42.195
dray kilometer tsu undzer dorf.

00:19:42.195 --> 00:19:44.635
ikh hob moyre gehat az emetser vet mir derzen

00:19:44.635 --> 00:19:46.745
un m'vet mir o- shrayen ZHYDIVKA.

00:19:47.083 --> 00:19:49.085
dervayl hot mir keyner nisht gezen.

00:19:49.125 --> 00:19:51.210
ikh hob zikh oyfgezetst oyf der ban.

00:19:51.210 --> 00:19:53.920
ikh hob geforn mit a groysn, groysn pakhed.

00:19:54.627 --> 00:19:58.553
zenen mir gekumen in a por sho keyn Ame- keyn Lemberik

00:19:58.592 --> 00:20:00.892
un zi hot shoyn gehat dort a bakante

00:20:00.892 --> 00:20:02.788
⟨vos ho'mir⟩ gegangen shlofn tsu ir.

00:20:02.794 --> 00:20:05.043
ikh hob dort ibergenekhtikt, yo?

00:20:05.043 --> 00:20:06.720
m'hot ibergenekhtikt

00:20:06.720 --> 00:20:10.381
un far nakht, dem tsveytn tog, greyt men zikh tsum tsug forn.

00:20:10.894 --> 00:20:12.713
me geyt tsum tsug forn.

00:20:12.713 --> 00:20:15.600
me geyt oyf der statsye. me fort mit dem tsug

00:20:15.600 --> 00:20:16.880
tsu STOYANOV.

00:20:17.104 --> 00:20:18.498
STOYANOV

00:20:18.657 --> 00:20:20.960
un dort iz geven a, di grenets

00:20:20.960 --> 00:20:23.560
dort iz geven der daytsh, un do iz geven der daytsh

00:20:23.560 --> 00:20:25.470
nor vos iz m'hot nisht durkhgelozt.

00:20:25.470 --> 00:20:27.327
m'hot badorfn shvartsn di grenets.

00:20:27.327 --> 00:20:30.660
dort hobn zey nisht gehat produktn ale. do iz geven

00:20:30.660 --> 00:20:34.203
mer farshidene zakhn, KAUSTIK tsu makhn zeyf

00:20:34.203 --> 00:20:37.365
naft hobn zey nisht gehat. heyvn hobn zey nisht gehat.

00:20:38.147 --> 00:20:44.806
hot zi, zogt zi azoy. zi hot gebrengt zakhn, un zi vet dos farkoyfn oykhet hot zi gezogt, nor ikh hob gornisht nisht gehat demolst

00:20:45.505 --> 00:20:52.434
mikh hot keyner nisht gevolt nemen tsu zikh. m'hot mir gegebn esn un trinken, oder keyner hot nisht gevolt, ikh hob nisht gehat keyn shum papirn, keyner hot mir nisht gevolt nemen.

00:20:52.693 --> 00:20:54.172
iz vos tu ikh?

00:20:54.398 --> 00:20:59.876
ikh nem, zi, zi hot mir farlozt. zi zogt "ikh ken shoyn mit dir nisht zayn. keyner vil dir nisht nemen."

00:21:00.118 --> 00:21:02.795
vos tu ikh? ikh gey tsu shtub tsu shtub

00:21:02.937 --> 00:21:04.216
mit a zekl

00:21:04.216 --> 00:21:05.884
un ikh nem tsuzamen broyt.

00:21:05.957 --> 00:21:08.055
un ikh zog azoy, "dos broyt

00:21:08.055 --> 00:21:13.435
vel ikh nemen in geto. ikh vel geyn tsurik in Boyberiker geto. s'iz geven ⟨LIFAKH-⟩ ikh zol hobn vos tsu esn.

00:21:13.435 --> 00:21:15.455
vifl ikh vel erlebn, ikh zol hobn vos tsu esn."

